79
00:04:33,439 --> 00:04:37,442
And, more importantly,
what does Souichiro Sama

80
00:04:37,443 --> 00:04:39,844
really mean to me?

81
00:04:39,845 --> 00:04:43,848
(machine clangs shut)

82
00:04:43,849 --> 00:04:46,352
(dog barking)

83
00:04:48,554 --> 00:04:51,323
(dramatic music)

84
00:04:59,498 --> 00:05:02,434
(footsteps on dirt)

85
00:05:04,303 --> 00:05:06,972
(flute playing)

86
00:05:09,008 --> 00:05:10,008
- Tagami.

87
00:05:11,076 --> 00:05:12,310
Why are you here?

88
00:05:12,311 --> 00:05:14,712
Did you get a call
from Isuzu as well?

89
00:05:14,713 --> 00:05:17,082
You're here 'cause of
the Juken Club, right?

90
00:05:18,250 --> 00:05:19,784
Tell me why you're here.

91
00:05:19,785 --> 00:05:22,620
I understood that I'd be
the executioner this time.

92
00:05:22,621 --> 00:05:26,290
I must say, I'm quite
displeased by this development.

93
00:05:26,291 --> 00:05:27,992
- I feel the same.

94
00:05:27,993 --> 00:05:30,895
We're in complete
agreement on this.

95
00:05:30,896 --> 00:05:33,531
To use so many of
us to attack so few,

96
00:05:33,532 --> 00:05:36,901
it goes against the
spirit of the samurai.

97
00:05:36,902 --> 00:05:39,337
- Then allow me to make this
a little easier for you.

98
00:05:39,338 --> 00:05:40,772
You are indeed strong enough

99
00:05:40,773 --> 00:05:42,808
to be within the
Executive Council.

100
00:05:43,942 --> 00:05:46,310
I'd want nothing less
from an opponent.

101
00:05:46,311 --> 00:05:48,479
(coat flapping in wind)

102
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:51,282
I think you and I should
determine right here and now

103
00:05:51,283 --> 00:05:55,219
which one of us is
the true executioner!

104
00:05:55,220 --> 00:05:56,687
(fist smacks)

105
00:05:56,688 --> 00:05:59,590
(growling)

106
00:05:59,591 --> 00:06:02,861
(dramatic violin music)

107
00:06:06,432 --> 00:06:10,169
(breathes loudly and slowly)

108
00:06:11,703 --> 00:06:12,738
- Stop it!

109
00:06:14,873 --> 00:06:16,707
I didn't order you two here just

110
00:06:16,708 --> 00:06:18,610
