fight each other.

111
00:06:23,749 --> 00:06:25,316
(sighs)

112
00:06:25,317 --> 00:06:27,451
- Miss Vice President,
do you really feel

113
00:06:27,452 --> 00:06:29,720
that I can't handle
this task alone?

114
00:06:29,721 --> 00:06:31,222
- That isn't the case.

115
00:06:31,223 --> 00:06:33,391
All that we're doing is
controlling the variables

116
00:06:33,392 --> 00:06:37,028
of this equation before the
situation becomes unmanageable.

117
00:06:37,029 --> 00:06:38,896
If we choose not
to act and instead

118
00:06:38,897 --> 00:06:40,565
let those two
freshmen go unchecked,

119
00:06:40,566 --> 00:06:41,832
they may very well prove

120
00:06:41,833 --> 00:06:43,801
to be a problem to
us in the future.

121
00:06:43,802 --> 00:06:45,169
- That's absolutely ridiculous.

122
00:06:45,170 --> 00:06:47,104
Those two are just a
couple of street thugs.

123
00:06:47,105 --> 00:06:49,740
- So, that's what
this is about, huh?

124
00:06:49,741 --> 00:06:53,244
- Don't tell me that you think
this is really necessary.

125
00:06:53,245 --> 00:06:55,746
- There is somebody
in the Juken Club

126
00:06:55,747 --> 00:06:57,548
who does pose a threat to us.

127
00:06:57,549 --> 00:07:00,018
In this particular
case, I agree.

128
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:03,821
- [Koji] Are you talking
about Takayanagi?

129
00:07:03,822 --> 00:07:06,123
I agree that he is
becoming strong, but...

130
00:07:06,124 --> 00:07:07,191
- Not him.

131
00:07:07,192 --> 00:07:09,593
You mean you haven't sensed it?

132
00:07:09,594 --> 00:07:13,064
You've never felt the power
of this individual before?

133
00:07:13,065 --> 00:07:15,032
I've just passed by this person,

134
00:07:15,033 --> 00:07:16,434
but that was more than enough.

135
00:07:16,435 --> 00:07:19,270
I was walking through
the school's courtyard.

136
00:07:19,271 --> 00:07:22,107
(leaves rustling)

137
00:07:26,611 --> 00:07:29,381
(dramatic noise)

138
00:07:30,816 --> 00:07:35,053
I've never seen eyes like
that before, on anyone.

139
00:07:36,221 --> 00:07:40,658
They were so deep, they
were endlessly deep,

140
00:07:40,659 --> 00:07:42,993
as if they could see everything

141
00:07:42,994 --> 00:07:46,397
and devour it all
in the process.

142
00:07:46,398 --> 00:07:49,134
(dramatic music)

143
00:07:51,970 --> 00:07:53,204
We must stop it.

144
00:07:53,205 --> 00:07:55,573
We can't allow those
powers to mature.

145
00:07:55,574 --> 00:07:57,441
I'm afraid that what
we're up against

146
00:07:57,442 --> 00:08:00,744
is an invincible power
heard of only in legends.

147
00:08:00,745 --> 00:08:02,012
Dragon Eye.

148
00:08:02,013 --> 00:08:03,347
- The Dragon Eye?

149
00:08:03,348 --> 00:08:05,850
- If we let this power
mature any longer,

150
00:08:05,851 --> 00:08:08,152
it will soon be
out of our control.

151
00:08:08,153 --> 00:08:12,456
So before that day
comes, I will defeat her.

152
00:08:12,457 --> 00:08:14,792
- I'd like to continue,
if you two don't mind.

153
00:08:14,793 --> 00:08:16,227
We're running out of time,

154
00:08:16,228 --> 00:08:17,895
and I still haven't
gotten to the main reason

155
00:08:17,896 --> 00:08:19,663
that I have called
you both here.

156
00:08:19,664 --> 00:08:21,365
The situation has changed.

157
00:08:21,366 --> 00:08:24,168
We're going to attack
the Juken Club tonight.

158
00:08:24,169 --> 00:08:25,703
- What are you talking about?

159
00:08:25,704 --> 00:08:28,772
- The president will be
on the move this evening.

160
00:08:28,773 --> 00:08:32,110
