166
00:09:03,174 --> 00:09:06,444
I have no doubt that Souichiro
Sama will start to hate me.

167
00:09:12,584 --> 00:09:15,252
- [Bob] We're in the
middle of golden week,

168
00:09:15,253 --> 00:09:16,253
